1
00:01:15,040 --> 00:01:17,079
Honey, I've had a lot on my plate lately

2
00:01:17,280 --> 00:01:18,239
I'm exhausted too

3
00:01:18,799 --> 00:01:20,200
But I swear to you

4
00:01:20,319 --> 00:01:21,640
I'm absolutely not the kind of

5
00:01:21,640 --> 00:01:22,680
fickle, unfaithful man

6
00:01:24,760 --> 00:01:26,000
I have a wife I love deeply

7
00:01:26,439 --> 00:01:27,439
and an adorable daughter

8
00:01:28,000 --> 00:01:29,280
No matter what she says

9
00:01:29,480 --> 00:01:30,159
or what she does

10
00:01:30,719 --> 00:01:32,079
it's all to get Fang Bing off the hook

11
00:01:33,560 --> 00:01:34,400
Honey

12
00:01:34,920 --> 00:01:36,319
Don't let her use you

13
00:01:50,560 --> 00:01:51,439
President Su

14
00:01:51,439 --> 00:01:54,040
The bank loan is about to come due

15
00:01:54,040 --> 00:01:56,200
They want a repayment plan from us

16
00:01:56,560 --> 00:01:57,680
Figure it out yourself

17
00:01:57,680 --> 00:01:58,599
Don't bother me

18
00:01:59,159 --> 00:02:00,000
President Su, this...

19
00:02:00,239 --> 00:02:01,359
this isn't appropriate, is it?

20
00:02:01,719 --> 00:02:02,719
Why isn't it appropriate?

21
00:02:02,719 --> 00:02:03,920
You're the Finance Director

22
00:02:04,400 --> 00:02:05,079
President Su

23
00:02:06,239 --> 00:02:06,840
Get out

24
00:02:08,840 --> 00:02:10,039
Draft the plan and bring it for my signature

25
00:02:17,719 --> 00:02:18,719
I told you to get out

26
00:02:19,439 --> 00:02:20,240
It's me

27
00:02:23,560 --> 00:02:24,439
What are you doing here?

28
00:02:24,719 --> 00:02:26,159
Things aren't messy enough for you?

29
00:02:26,840 --> 00:02:28,240
The situation is critical

30
00:02:28,479 --> 00:02:29,800
Why are you losing your temper?

31
00:02:30,599 --> 00:02:32,080
Then what should I do?

32
00:02:32,719 --> 00:02:34,639
Any news from Fang Bing?

33
00:02:36,520 --> 00:02:37,240
Fishing for information?

34
00:02:37,879 --> 00:02:39,840
Or trying to use Fang Bing to claim a reward?

35
00:02:40,439 --> 00:02:41,080
Let me tell you

36
00:02:41,080 --> 00:02:42,039
If Fang Bing goes to prison

37
00:02:42,039 --> 00:02:43,039
you won't get off easy either

38
00:02:43,280 --> 00:02:44,240
That's not what I meant

39
00:02:46,120 --> 00:02:47,479
I just wanted to say

40
00:02:47,680 --> 00:02:48,919
I've helped you two so much

41
00:02:49,400 --> 00:02:50,240
Now I need some money

42
00:02:50,240 --> 00:02:51,039
Give me some

43
00:02:53,439 --> 00:02:55,199
Han Lin, the nerve of you!

44
00:02:56,439 --> 00:02:58,039
You set me up on Plot No. 6

45
00:02:58,039 --> 00:02:59,479
and made me lose a fortune

46
00:02:59,800 --> 00:03:02,560
On Plot 7 General Contracting, you framed
Fang Bing and made him a wanted man.

47
00:03:03,400 --> 00:03:04,639
You've reduced the two of us

48
00:03:04,639 --> 00:03:06,039
to this state, it's all your fault

49
00:03:06,240 --> 00:03:07,400
And you have the gall to ask for money?

50
00:03:07,879 --> 00:03:09,319
How can you say that?

51
00:03:09,599 --> 00:03:11,039
Fang Bing was the one who kidnapped him

52
00:03:11,240 --> 00:03:12,520
Did I force him to do it?

53
00:03:13,719 --> 00:03:14,120
Get out!

54
00:03:14,840 --> 00:03:15,439
Get out!

55
00:03:15,520 --> 00:03:18,560
Get out!

56
00:03:18,560 --> 00:03:19,800
You lunatic!

57
00:03:20,360 --> 00:03:21,080
Get out!

58
00:03:22,039 --> 00:03:22,919
Ah!

59
00:03:31,400 --> 00:03:33,240
Li Yao took a knife for you

60
00:03:33,240 --> 00:03:35,680
which proves he's not a bad person at heart

61
00:03:36,120 --> 00:03:37,479
Once he recovers and turns himself in

62
00:03:38,039 --> 00:03:39,800
we'll see how the police handle it

63
00:03:40,039 --> 00:03:40,680
Chairman Zheng

64
00:03:41,120 --> 00:03:42,039
I was thinking

65
00:03:42,319 --> 00:03:43,479
once Li Yao is a free man

66
00:03:43,879 --> 00:03:44,759
at our company

67
00:03:45,120 --> 00:03:46,000
we could arrange a job for him

68
00:03:47,280 --> 00:03:48,520
Well, that's quite generous of you

69
00:03:49,080 --> 00:03:50,479
Will He Junjie accept it?

70
00:03:52,479 --> 00:03:53,599
Li Yao's confession for leniency

71
00:03:54,520 --> 00:03:56,080
the victim's letter of forgiveness

72
00:03:56,680 --> 00:03:58,479
plus, at the critical moment,

73
00:03:58,719 --> 00:03:59,879
Li Yao stepping forward

74
00:04:00,639 --> 00:04:02,840
proves he's not a bad person at heart

75
00:04:03,800 --> 00:04:04,360
Well said

76
00:04:05,280 --> 00:04:06,439
Then for Plot No. 7

77
00:04:06,439 --> 00:04:07,599
the Phase One General Contracting work

78
00:04:07,919 --> 00:04:08,840
how do you plan to handle it?

79
00:04:09,719 --> 00:04:10,560
I'm leaving on a business trip tomorrow

80
00:04:10,879 --> 00:04:11,719
We'll decide when I get back

81
00:04:12,319 --> 00:04:12,719
Okay

82
00:04:13,039 --> 00:04:13,400
Okay

83
00:04:14,520 --> 00:04:15,120
I'll be on my way then

84
00:04:24,959 --> 00:04:25,399
Bai Li.

85
00:04:25,600 --> 00:04:26,199
Bai Li.

86
00:04:26,399 --> 00:04:26,839
Bai Li.

87
00:04:27,040 --> 00:04:27,639
What is it?

88
00:04:27,759 --> 00:04:28,079
Bai Li.

89
00:04:30,639 --> 00:04:31,439
I'm begging you.

90
00:04:31,439 --> 00:04:32,839
Get Mr. He to sign a letter of forgiveness.

91
00:04:33,279 --> 00:04:34,079
In your dreams.

92
00:04:34,319 --> 00:04:35,120
My husband is still

93
00:04:35,120 --> 00:04:36,399
lying in the hospital.

94
00:04:38,680 --> 00:04:39,040
But...

95
00:04:39,040 --> 00:04:40,279
But it was Li Yao who had

96
00:04:40,519 --> 00:04:41,319
someone hit your husband.

97
00:04:41,360 --> 00:04:43,000
It wasn't Fang Bing who did it.

98
00:04:43,199 --> 00:04:44,800
You wrote Li Yao a letter of forgiveness,

99
00:04:44,800 --> 00:04:45,360
so why can't you

100
00:04:45,360 --> 00:04:46,519
write one for Fang Bing too?

101
00:04:47,600 --> 00:04:48,920
You two really are

102
00:04:48,920 --> 00:04:49,920
an unbelievable couple.

103
00:04:50,160 --> 00:04:51,680
One tries to climb into Xiao Yifan's bed,

104
00:04:52,040 --> 00:04:53,000
the other kidnaps my son.

105
00:04:53,319 --> 00:04:53,639
Do you think

106
00:04:53,639 --> 00:04:55,240
your family owns Loujiang City?

107
00:04:55,720 --> 00:04:56,879
With all the evil you've done,

108
00:04:56,959 --> 00:04:58,680
won't you be struck by lightning?

109
00:04:59,360 --> 00:05:00,879
Fang Bing lost his mind,

110
00:05:01,439 --> 00:05:02,759
but he'll never do it again.

111
00:05:03,160 --> 00:05:03,839
I'm begging you.

112
00:05:03,839 --> 00:05:04,920
Please write him a letter of forgiveness.

113
00:05:04,920 --> 00:05:05,839
Please?

114
00:05:07,040 --> 00:05:08,600
You're so eager to clear Fang Bing's name.

115
00:05:08,879 --> 00:05:09,439
Anyone watching

116
00:05:09,439 --> 00:05:10,800
would think you two are deeply in love.

117
00:05:13,040 --> 00:05:14,480
He didn't mean to harm you.

118
00:05:14,839 --> 00:05:16,000
He was egged on by someone else.

119
00:05:16,560 --> 00:05:17,800
He'll never do it again.

120
00:05:17,800 --> 00:05:19,279
Please, give him a way out.

121
00:05:20,199 --> 00:05:21,399
Don't pull any of your tricks.

122
00:05:21,439 --> 00:05:22,240
I'm not buying it.

123
00:05:23,360 --> 00:05:23,879
Hey.

124
00:05:25,120 --> 00:05:25,759
Bai Li.

125
00:05:26,240 --> 00:05:26,800
Bai Li.

126
00:05:26,959 --> 00:05:27,439
Bai Li.

127
00:05:38,839 --> 00:05:39,920
How are you feeling?

128
00:05:42,120 --> 00:05:43,199
Honey.

129
00:05:43,439 --> 00:05:44,560
Why are you sweating so much?

130
00:05:45,079 --> 00:05:45,879
It's hot outside.

131
00:05:46,240 --> 00:05:47,480
And that Su Yuanyuan,

132
00:05:47,480 --> 00:05:49,360
she stopped me, asking you to give

133
00:05:49,360 --> 00:05:50,319
her husband a letter of forgiveness.

134
00:05:50,319 --> 00:05:51,600
I don't know where she gets the nerve.

135
00:05:52,560 --> 00:05:53,800
Here, eat it while it's hot.

136
00:05:55,879 --> 00:05:56,560
Honey.

137
00:05:57,639 --> 00:05:59,240
After all, they're husband and wife.

138
00:06:00,639 --> 00:06:02,480
I can't finish all this food.

139
00:06:02,560 --> 00:06:04,079
Let's share some with Li Yao.

140
00:06:04,800 --> 00:06:06,199
Why should he get any?

141
00:06:06,480 --> 00:06:08,959
I got up early to make this soup for you.

142
00:06:09,319 --> 00:06:10,279
If you won't eat it, I will.

143
00:06:10,360 --> 00:06:11,839
I've never met anyone as naive as you.

144
00:06:12,240 --> 00:06:12,879
Honey.

145
00:06:13,439 --> 00:06:15,160
Li Yao did it to save Xiao Yifan,

146
00:06:15,839 --> 00:06:17,639
and Xiao Yifan saved our son.

147
00:06:18,120 --> 00:06:19,439
A bowl of bone soup isn't too much to ask.

148
00:06:20,959 --> 00:06:21,720
If you want to go, you go.

149
00:06:21,720 --> 00:06:23,279
I'm not that kind-hearted.

150
00:06:26,519 --> 00:06:27,879
Fine, I'll go.

151
00:06:28,079 --> 00:06:29,879
You're really serious?

152
00:06:31,040 --> 00:06:32,040
You're unbelievable.

153
00:06:33,639 --> 00:06:35,160
I'll take it and share it with Li Yao.

154
00:06:35,720 --> 00:06:37,040
Let me help you over there.

155
00:06:39,639 --> 00:06:40,120
Let's go.

156
00:06:40,560 --> 00:06:41,360
Take it slow.

157
00:07:32,720 --> 00:07:34,120
Sister-in-law, thank you.

158
00:07:34,680 --> 00:07:36,279
Don't. Don't call me that.

159
00:07:36,279 --> 00:07:38,120
You hired someone to run my husband down.

160
00:07:39,000 --> 00:07:41,000
I don't deserve to be called that.

161
00:07:41,720 --> 00:07:42,879
That's enough, honey.

162
00:07:43,079 --> 00:07:44,160
Go get some rest.

163
00:07:44,160 --> 00:07:45,319
You've had a long day.

164
00:07:45,319 --> 00:07:45,759
Okay.

165
00:07:46,199 --> 00:07:46,920
I'll go ask the doctor

166
00:07:46,920 --> 00:07:47,920
when you can be discharged.

167
00:07:51,800 --> 00:07:52,439
Mr. He,

168
00:07:53,720 --> 00:07:54,360
I'm sorry.

169
00:07:55,240 --> 00:07:56,160
I nearly got you killed.

170
00:07:57,240 --> 00:07:58,040
It's fine, it's fine.

171
00:07:58,560 --> 00:07:59,759
Yifan already told me everything.

172
00:08:00,199 --> 00:08:01,480
I've written the letter of forgiveness.

173
00:08:02,079 --> 00:08:02,759
If you keep this up,

174
00:08:02,839 --> 00:08:03,839
I'll take it back.

175
00:08:05,720 --> 00:08:06,439
Thank you.

176
00:08:07,759 --> 00:08:08,360
Mr. He,

177
00:08:09,439 --> 00:08:10,879
I never expected you, like Mr. Xiao,

178
00:08:10,879 --> 00:08:11,879
to be so forgiving.

179
00:08:13,800 --> 00:08:15,079
Eat first.

180
00:08:17,560 --> 00:08:18,920
You still have a long road ahead.

181
00:08:19,639 --> 00:08:20,839
What you've been through,

182
00:08:21,160 --> 00:08:22,399
Yifan and I have been through it too.

183
00:08:23,120 --> 00:08:23,839
From now on,

184
00:08:24,399 --> 00:08:25,560
live an honest life.

185
00:08:26,360 --> 00:08:26,959
Thank you.

186
00:08:37,320 --> 00:08:38,559
I can manage on my own.

187
00:08:44,440 --> 00:08:46,720
Now you come crying to me?

188
00:08:47,240 --> 00:08:48,440
Where were you before?

189
00:08:50,679 --> 00:08:51,320
Auntie,

190
00:08:51,679 --> 00:08:52,559
you have connections.

191
00:08:52,679 --> 00:08:53,960
Please help Fang Bing.

192
00:08:54,600 --> 00:08:56,080
Once he's back, I won't cause trouble anymore.

193
00:08:56,080 --> 00:08:58,080
I'll live a proper life with him.

194
00:08:58,440 --> 00:08:59,240
Help him?

195
00:09:00,600 --> 00:09:02,399
With all the illegal things he's done,

196
00:09:02,399 --> 00:09:03,480
who would dare help him?

197
00:09:04,639 --> 00:09:06,120
His company accounts are frozen now,

198
00:09:06,480 --> 00:09:07,879
and my cash flow is broken too.

199
00:09:08,360 --> 00:09:09,919
You should pay me back!

200
00:09:11,480 --> 00:09:12,360
Fang Bing is in this state now.

201
00:09:12,360 --> 00:09:13,679
Where would I get the money to pay you?

202
00:09:16,559 --> 00:09:18,120
You only think about yourselves.

203
00:09:18,519 --> 00:09:18,799
Huh?

204
00:09:19,159 --> 00:09:19,879
I have no money now.

205
00:09:19,879 --> 00:09:20,440
How am I supposed to answer

206
00:09:20,440 --> 00:09:21,399
to the shareholders behind me?

207
00:09:22,480 --> 00:09:23,240
Do you think being

208
00:09:23,240 --> 00:09:23,919
the head of a company

209
00:09:23,919 --> 00:09:24,879
is that easy?

210
00:09:26,200 --> 00:09:27,120
Don't push me.

211
00:09:27,679 --> 00:09:28,559
The bank is still waiting

212
00:09:28,559 --> 00:09:29,639
for my repayment plan.

213
00:09:30,279 --> 00:09:31,440
You don't need to tell me all this.

214
00:09:31,919 --> 00:09:32,559
Let me tell you,

215
00:09:33,080 --> 00:09:34,159
if you don't pay me back,

216
00:09:34,679 --> 00:09:36,480
I'll take Wanhe Manor Phase Two's units

217
00:09:36,480 --> 00:09:37,480
and put them up as collateral.

218
00:09:37,799 --> 00:09:39,200
I'll notify the Legal Department now

219
00:09:39,200 --> 00:09:40,080
to handle the paperwork.

220
00:09:42,879 --> 00:09:44,360
Are you even human?

221
00:09:44,360 --> 00:09:46,440
Kicking me when I'm down!

222
00:09:46,440 --> 00:09:48,879
Never speak to your elder this way.

223
00:09:49,559 --> 00:09:50,600
Let me tell you,

224
00:09:51,279 --> 00:09:52,960
Fang Bing ending up like this today,

225
00:09:53,080 --> 00:09:55,039
you bear unavoidable responsibility.

226
00:09:56,039 --> 00:09:58,080
As his wife, you failed to manage him.

227
00:09:58,080 --> 00:10:00,519
As a boss, you failed to run the company.

228
00:10:00,519 --> 00:10:02,120
Don't you think you're a failure?

229
00:10:02,120 --> 00:10:04,120
Do you think I wanted this?

230
00:10:04,320 --> 00:10:06,919
You're his aunt. You're responsible too.

231
00:10:07,039 --> 00:10:08,440
I have responsibility?

232
00:10:08,559 --> 00:10:09,080
Fine.

233
00:10:09,200 --> 00:10:10,240
Saying more now is useless.

234
00:10:10,240 --> 00:10:11,159
Let me tell you,

235
00:10:11,559 --> 00:10:12,879
your only option now

236
00:10:13,200 --> 00:10:15,240
is to go find He Junjie and Xiao Yifan,

237
00:10:15,399 --> 00:10:16,720
and beg them for letters of forgiveness.

238
00:10:16,879 --> 00:10:17,639
Do you understand?

239
00:10:18,679 --> 00:10:21,720
Yang Hui and Bai Li refused to see me.

240
00:10:21,879 --> 00:10:23,279
I'll say it again.

241
00:10:23,279 --> 00:10:25,720
Go to He Junjie and Xiao Yifan.

242
00:10:25,720 --> 00:10:28,120
Cry and kneel before them till you die.

243
00:10:28,120 --> 00:10:30,679
Their forgiveness is your only way out.

244
00:10:30,679 --> 00:10:31,720
Do you understand?
